Body.hs_brev:
DPA
Level 3 to 5-awarded to procurement specialists in designated
procurement posts based on an individual's skills, experience and
qualifications. DPA Level 3 allows purchasing up to the EU Threshold;
DWP Level 4 to above the EU threshold up to  £5 million;
and DPA level 5 above £5 million.
